Files of interest:

lexgen.doc		- User's manual for Mythryl-Lex
lexgen.sml		- ML version of Lex
export-lex.sml          - implements an exportable (via lib7.spawn_to_disk)
			  toplevel driver for Mythryl-Lex;  the resulting
			  stand-alone program takes the specification
			  file name as a command line argument
mythryl-lex.lib	- makelib library definition file for Mythryl-Lex
build			- script that invokes ../../bin/build-an-executable-mythryl-heap-image
			  in order to construct the executable program image for Mythryl-Lex
